  1‚Üí/**
  2‚Üí * FDC Trusted Relayer ‚Äî Sapphire Accounting Demo
  3‚Üí *
  4‚Üí * End-to-end flow:
  5‚Üí * 1. Deploy FdcAccounting contract on Sapphire (or connect to existing)
  6‚Üí * 2. Run FDC attestation for a Sepolia tx via Coston2
  7‚Üí * 3. Verify the Merkle proof on-chain
  8‚Üí * 4. Relay verified deposit to the Sapphire accounting contract
  9‚Üí * 5. Query the depositor's private balance
 10‚Üí */
 11‚Üí
